{{en-infl-reg-other-e|purpos|e||}}

#{{transitive}} Have set as one's purpose; [[resolve]] to [[accomplish]]; [[intend]]; [[plan]].
# {{transitive}} (''passive'') [[designed|Designed]] for some purpose.

